  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Mortal Kombat: Deadly Alliance is a 2002 fighting game developed and published by Midway for the Xbox, PlayStation 2, GameCube, and Game Boy Advance. This is the Game Boy Advance port. It was the first all-new Mortal Kombat fighting game produced exclusively for home consoles, with no preceding arcade release.",
